                        	<p>By using this site, you agree to the forfeit of your:</p>
                        	<ol>
                            	<li>soul, or</li>
                            	<li>first-born child</li>
                        	</ol>
                        	<p>to Eevee, or at His Dark Voraciousness' discretion, both. Failure to comply will result in being publicly gamed on.</p>
